&gt;&gt; David R Castillo:
Bueno, hello everyone,

00:05:28.190 --> 00:05:30.830
it's a great pleasure
to be here talking

00:05:30.830 --> 00:05:33.510
about this wonderful
collaboration

00:05:33.510 --> 00:05:37.200
that Will and I have worked on.

00:05:37.200 --> 00:05:40.470
The collaboration itself was
wonderful and the results,

00:05:40.470 --> 00:05:43.390
it's for you to judge
