00:05:54.660 --> 00:05:57.660
to the Rescue" [audience
laughter] and now we're

00:05:57.660 --> 00:06:02.880
on record, so we have
to go ahead and do

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:04.180
that [audience laughter].

