00:30:19.890 --> 00:30:24.020
and they're made with a
combination of printed page,

00:30:24.020 --> 00:30:26.440
so using the printing
press and woodcuts

00:30:26.440 --> 00:30:28.740
and the woodcuts are
very high quality.

00:30:28.740 --> 00:30:31.460
This is from SebastiÃ¡n
de Covarrubias whose also

00:30:31.460 --> 00:30:32.950
well-known for having
produced one

00:30:32.950 --> 00:30:36.290
of the most important
dictionaries of the time,

00:30:36.290 --> 00:30:38.550
the Diccionario de Autoridades.

00:30:38.550 --> 00:30:41.390
And so, we'll take
an example here

00:30:41.390 --> 00:30:45.390
so that I can actually
