great satanic fisher of souls.

00:32:30.370 --> 00:32:33.500
So, just as people's proper
protection requires the

00:32:33.500 --> 00:32:37.690
self-sacrifice of the sovereign
in the previous emblem,

00:32:37.690 --> 00:32:40.120
this emblem directs its
reader toward the sacrifice

00:32:40.120 --> 00:32:42.400
of his own pleasure, linking

00:32:42.400 --> 00:32:45.050
