to damnation.

00:32:45.050 --> 00:32:49.060
A watchful, prudent eye must
be watchful first and foremost

00:32:49.060 --> 00:32:52.920
of its own desires is the
message that we're meant

00:32:52.920 --> 00:32:55.090
to receive from this emblem.

00:32:55.090 --> 00:32:56.940
We can see the positive
counterpart

00:32:56.940 --> 00:33:01.320
