life says the whip,

00:34:46.030 --> 00:34:48.170
but it also specifies
the kind of students

00:34:48.170 --> 00:34:50.900
who will benefit from its rigor.

00:34:50.900 --> 00:34:53.320
The word specifically
is "lerdos",

00:34:53.320 --> 00:34:55.400
the oafs and the slow witted.

00:34:55.400 --> 00:34:57.770
Those, in other words, who
haven't the self-discipline

00:34:57.770 --> 00:35:01.060
to tame themselves will
benefit and even gain life

00:35:01.060 --> 00:35:03.680
from punishment, but
not all students need

00:35:03.680 --> 00:35:05.030
to be shaped in this way.

00:35:05.030 --> 00:35:07.960
As Covarrubias writes in another
emblem dedicated to the theme

00:35:07.960 --> 00:35:11.890
