so it's in the very same book.

00:35:11.890 --> 00:35:13.970
In fact, it's only
separated by a few pages.

00:35:13.970 --> 00:35:17.360
Teachers should spare the
whip on well-born children

00:35:17.360 --> 00:35:18.810
for whom its rigors
are more likely

00:35:18.810 --> 00:35:21.740
to cause their generous spirits,
naturally generous spirits

00:35:21.740 --> 00:35:25.920
