men, kinds of people,

00:35:39.020 --> 00:35:41.350
already present in
their children.

00:35:41.350 --> 00:35:44.130
There are those whose blood
destines them to be leaders,

00:35:44.130 --> 00:35:46.680
whose natural generosity
makes the imposition

00:35:46.680 --> 00:35:50.180
of suffering unnecessary and
even potentially detrimental

00:35:50.180 --> 00:35:53.580
and for these, literally in
Spanish, sons of something,

00:35:53.580 --> 00:35:58.770
"Hidalgos" the base term
for the gentry of the time,

00:35:58.770 --> 00:36:02.030
literally signified already
having something in them,

00:36:02.030 --> 00:36:05.950
a proclivity to choose
suffering over pleasure.

00:36:05.950 --> 00:36:09.390
It is meanwhile the oafish,
the weak, those lacking

00:36:09.390 --> 00:36:11.700
in such natural attributes,
such lineage,

00:36:11.700 --> 00:36:15.220
who should not be spared
the lash if only out of duty

00:36:15.220 --> 00:36:19.500
and compassion for their likely
fate, free from its scar.

00:36:19.500 --> 00:36:22.840
So, what I think to draw us back
to the contemporary applications

00:36:22.840 --> 00:36:26.220
that David was making
in the opening,

00:36:26.220 --> 00:36:31.800
this should make us think about
the assumptions of neutrality,

00:36:31.800 --> 00:36:36.140
immediacy, equality
that lead one to assume

00:36:36.140 --> 00:36:40.250
that one's position, for
example, in life is a direct

00:36:40.250 --> 00:36:45.070
and unmediated expression
