00:36:59.460 --> 00:37:03.740
of filters that determine our
notions of guilt, of innocence,

00:37:03.740 --> 00:37:06.580
of virtue and responsibility,
and the point

00:37:06.580 --> 00:37:09.000
of the book then is to show
how the very strategies

00:37:09.000 --> 00:37:12.340
