unaltered in any way,"

00:37:20.780 --> 00:37:25.440
are in fact not dependent
specifically on technologies,

00:37:25.440 --> 00:37:29.240
but rather are built into
the way that old technologies

00:37:29.240 --> 00:37:33.750
as well are perfectly capable
of manipulating reality.

